Class TryReadLastConfirmedOp

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.bookkeeper.client.TryReadLastConfirmedOp

    org.apache.bookkeeper.proto.BookkeeperInternalCallbacks.ReadEntryCallback

    class TryReadLastConfirmedOp
extends Object
implements org.apache.bookkeeper.proto.BookkeeperInternalCallbacks.ReadEntryCallback
    This op is try to read last confirmed without involving quorum coverage checking. Use ReadLastConfirmedOp if you need quorum coverage checking.
